{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十三回 庆功宴上。龟兹王为胡铁花等人设庆功宴，胡铁花将\"极乐之星\"归还龟兹王，龟兹王却将其赠予胡铁花。龟兹王揭示\"极乐之星\"的秘密实为他故意散布的谣言，以便暗中完成复国大业。琵琶公主埋怨父亲隐瞒真相，龟兹王解释为保护自身安全。姬冰雁批评龟兹王利用镖客送死，龟兹王以军国政治的残酷辩解。胡铁花感叹帝王寂寞，不如平民自在。龟兹王妃突然出现，揭示其真实身份为石观音，原来她已杀死真正的龟兹王妃并取而代之。石观音透露自己下毒谋害龟兹王父女，并已毒倒青胡子的手下。青胡子愤怒攻击，却被胡铁花阻止，因为胡铁花看出石观音武功深不可测。石观音展示其绝技\"男人见不得\"，胡铁花和姬冰雁均无法破解，众人陷入绝境。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子莫不是为了怕被多情的公主缠上，竟偷偷溜了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只当别人也和你一样么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼!我看靠不住，这小子什么事都做得出，咱们不如先去找他吧!",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，就这么办。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极乐之星",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极乐之星",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "壮士大功，小王无以为酬，就将这宝石送给你，以为留念吧!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极乐之星",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这穷小子身上若有了如此珍贵的东西，以后还想睡得着觉么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这宝石岂非关系着一件极大的秘密么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就叫明修栈道，暗渡陈仓的声东击西之计。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪楚留香一直觉得奇怪，这",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来一个人若是做了国王的女儿，也不是什么幸运的事，难怪前朝某公主临死的时候要掩面大哭，说：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "军国政治，本就是件可怕的事，一将功成，尚且枯骨盈出，何况一国之君呢?这本是自古以来，不可避免的悲惨之事，贤如唐宋开国帝王，也未能免此，先生又何必独罪本王?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下一时失言，还望王爷恕罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一句：'且饮杯中酒，莫问身后事'，但'狡兔死，走狗烹，飞鸟尽，良弓藏'，这句话你难道就未听说过么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎地也来了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王妃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来了，你不高兴么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但你身子单薄，又怎禁得起如此风寒之苦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫说这区区寒风冷露，就算是刀风箭雨，王妃也不会放在眼里的，是么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王妃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸟尽弓藏，兔死狗烹，王妃莫非已想将咱们宰了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王绝无此意，各位也不必多虑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王妃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽无此意，我却有这意思了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认得我么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎会不认得你?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王妃",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却认得你，你就是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王妃",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新娘子",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王妃",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "石观音!你就是石观音了!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不管你是谁，但我的王妃……你难道竟杀了她么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也用不着难受，她虽然死了，但我却没有死，难道我还是比不上她?你难道还不满意?",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我既已代替了她，自然就会永远代替下去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我也知道她一定会永远代替下去的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你知道?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要杀我?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你难道已在酒中下了毒?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下的虽不多，但已足够你父女两人用的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可是想出去找帮手么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，你莫忘了我手下还有八百兄弟，俱是身经百战，绝不怕死的好男儿，就凭你一人之力，要想将咱们杀光，只怕还不容易，只要咱们有一个人活着，你的诡计就休想成功，我劝你还是打消这主意吧!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_hu_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青胡子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道也在他们的酒中下了毒?他们竟会没有一个人瞧见?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我方才在你面前下了毒?你可瞧见了么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "身经百战",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡壮士，你怎地也反了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你疯了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道不是小王爷的朋友?你为何要打我?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你为什么要向咱们出手?难道你也是她的同党?还是你见机不对，就想迎风转舵，投到她那一边去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你救了他们反而挨骂，又何苦多事呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他救的是你，不是我，若不是他多事，你现在还有命么?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为就凭你们那两招就能伤得了我?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么伤不了你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真是个不知天多高、地多厚的小孩子，为什么不想想，你们方才那一招若真使得不错，胡铁花怎能在举手间就将你们制住?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看，我现在使的这一招若在方才使出来，你们还活得成么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你救了他们，可也自己想来和我动手么?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你方才使用的那是什么武功?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我告诉你也无妨，那一招叫做'男人见不得'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人见不得?这算什么武功?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这又是哪一门，哪一派的武功?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    }
  ],
